siren

Class EmbeddedLinkSubEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • siren.EntityBase
      • siren.EmbeddedLinkSubEntity

  • public class EmbeddedLinkSubEntity
extends EntityBase
    A sub-entity containing an href value. One difference is that a sub-entity MUST contain a rel attribute to describe its relationship to the parent entity.
    Since:
    8/13/17
    Author:
    jonfreer
